  "title": "feat(infiniteHits): support new routing system",
  "body": "This updates `infiniteHits` lifecycle methods to support the new routing system.\r\n\r\nI'm not aware of how the new routing system will exactly work, so this behavior needs to be reviewed.\r\n\r\n## `getWidgetState` changes\r\n\r\nThis method ignores previous UI state values. Otherwise, new values gets skipped.\r\n\r\n## `getWidgetSearchParameters` changes\r\n\r\nThis method now also supports highlighting tags.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n_`getConfiguration` will be removed later to not break everything._",
